<p><strong>Why eligibility matters:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Prevents over-borrowing beyond your means</li>
<li>Speeds up application processing</li>
<li>Improves your chances of approval</li>
<li>Helps you get better interest rates</li>
<li>Avoids wasting time on unsuitable lenders</li>
