<p><strong>Foreign Residents:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Minimum age: 21 years old</li>
<li>Maximum age: 55-60 years (stricter than locals)</li>
<li>Must have at least 2-3 years remaining on visa</li>
<li>Loan tenure cannot exceed visa expiry</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Age considerations:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Younger applicants (21-25): May need guarantor or higher income</li>
<li>Prime age (26-50): Best approval rates and terms</li>
