<p><strong>Included Income:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Basic salary (100% counted)</li>
<li>Fixed allowances (transport, housing - 100% counted)</li>
<li>Overtime pay (50-70% counted due to variability)</li>
<li>Commission income (30-50% counted)</li>
<li>Rental income (70-80% counted after expenses)</li>
<li>Investment dividends (varies by stability)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Excluded Income:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bonus payments (unpredictable)</li>
